org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.router

Class RouterMetrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.router.RouterMetrics

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @Metrics(about="Metrics for Router Federation Interceptor",
         context="fedr")
public final class RouterMetrics
extends Object
    This class is for maintaining the various Router Federation Interceptor activity statistics and publishing them through the metrics interfaces.
